  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some of the cool features on Google now?",
  "response": "As of the latest updates, Google Now as a standalone service has been replaced and integrated into various Google services, primarily Google Assistant. Google Assistant now encompasses many of the features that were originally part of Google Now. Here are some cool features and functionalities currently available through Google Assistant and related Google services:\n\n1. **Voice Commands**: You can perform tasks such as sending texts, setting reminders, and getting directions using voice commands.\n\n2. **Smart Home Integration**: Google Assistant can control smart home devices like lights, thermostats, and security cameras.\n\n3. **Reminders and Alarms**: You can set location-based and time-based reminders, and alarms using natural language processing.\n\n4. **Routine Scheduling**: Create custom routines that perform multiple tasks with a single command, like \"Good morning\" to turn on lights, play the news, and give you a commute update.\n\n5. **Real-time Language Translation**: Use the interpreter mode for real-time language translation during conversations.\n\n6. **Personalized Recommendations**: Get personalized updates on weather, traffic, and news based on your preferences and routine.\n\n7. **Snapshot Feature**: Provides a daily summary of your schedule, commute time, and other personalized updates.\n\n8. **Integration with Apps**: Google Assistant can integrate with third-party apps, allowing you to perform tasks like booking a ride or ordering food.\n\n9. **Broadcast Feature**: Send messages across all your Google Home or Nest devices to communicate with family members.\n\n10. **Music and Media Control**: Control music playback on various streaming services and manage other media content.\n\n11. **Calendar Management**: Access and manage your schedule directly through Google Assistant.\n\n12. **Shopping List Management**: Add items to your grocery list using voice commands and manage them across devices.\n\nKeep in mind that features can vary based on the device, region, and Google's latest updates or changes.",
